  "observation": "Brainstorm triggered by plateau. 4 proposals generated.",
  "suggestion": "The plateau is not a failure of the learning algorithm—it's exhaustion of degrees of freedom. The system has explored all local optima within its current architectural constraints. Single organisms, single beauty metric, static environment = 3 hard walls. Each proposal removes one wall. The deepest insight: evolution stalls not because selection is weak, but because the design space itself is bounded. Unbounded search spaces have no plateau.; [easy] Multi-dimensional beauty space with orthogonal aesthetic metrics — Current system likely optimizes single beauty dimension to saturation (e.g., symmetry or color). Add independent beauty axes: structural elegance, motion grace, metabolic efficiency grace, growth pattern complexity. Organisms stuck at local optima on one axis can now explore orthogonal dimensions. Fitness plateau was 1D optimization solved; 3D space is fresh. Requires beauty evaluation to composite across uncorrelated metrics.; [hard] Obligate symbiosis / colonial organism formation as heritable trait — Current evolution optimizes single organisms. Add trait that allows organisms to form genetically linked colonies (multi-cell organism equivalents) that survive as units, reproduce as units, and accumulate beauty/efficiency bonuses from collective behavior. Evolution shifts from individual-scale to collective-scale architecture. New body plans, division of labor, emergent behaviors become possible. Fitness plateau was at organism scale; colony scale opens unexplored design space.; [medium] Cyclic environmental pressure: seasonal resource scarcity and predation waves — Current world is static; organisms optimized for fixed conditions never adapt. Add 50-100 cycle seasons with: (1) resource drought phases, (2) predator population spikes, (3) temperature extremes. Organisms optimized for avg conditions become suboptimal when environment shifts. Constant pressure to evolve generalist strategies, bet-hedging, dormancy, rapid reproduction switching. Static landscape fitness plateau → dynamic landscape perpetual novelty. Beauty becomes context-dependent.",
